public class WeightedTransition<NodeType>
extends Transition<NodeType>
implements java.lang.Comparable<WeightedTransition<NodeType>>

A relation that supports storing two more pieces of information with a transition: the fraction of all events that take this transition, and the number of events that this transition. The fraction is the count divided by the number of events belonging to the source node.

Author:
Sigurd Schneider
